snippet.title: Bare Butt Boxing - Early Access Announcement Trailer
snippet.description:
Wishlist on Steam : https://store.steampowered.com/app/1186660/Bare_Butt_Boxing/

Bare Butt Boxing will be available in Early Access May 4th 2023!

Be one of the first to join in on the fun with this colorful physics based brawler.
Take control of mischievous aliens mesmerized by the sport of boxing as they battle it out all over our beloved planet Earth, unaware of the laws and traditions of human society.

Join us on Discord : https://discord.com/invite/GTa9eQptHC
Follow us on Twitter : https://twitter.com/BareButtBoxing
About us : https://tuataragames.com/
